      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Kad un Rabsakus atpakkat\nnahze / tad atradde wiꞥſch to\nKehninu no Affirijas prett Libun\nkarrojam/ jo wiꞥſch bij dsirdejs/\nka tas no Lakifa bija aigabjis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Un kad wiꞥſch no Tiraka\nfi un to Semmi darrijs.\nto Mohru Kehninna dsirdeja/ ka\nfazzibts ktua/ raugi/ wiꞥſch irr\nisgabjis ar tew karroht/ tad fuh-\ntija wiꞥſch attak Wehstnefchus\npee Iſtiju/ un fazzija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Ta runnajt us Iſtiju to\nKehninu no Juha/ un fakkajt:\nLai taws Deews terw ne peewilt/\nus ko tu pataujees / fazzidans:\nJerusaleme ne taps tam Kehni-\nnain no Affirijas eedohta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Rangi/ tu effi dsirdejs/ ko\ntee Affirenu Kehnint wiſſahm\nSemnehm darrijschi tahs tsdel-\ndedami/ un tew bij isglahbtam\ntapt?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Irrag to Paganzu Dee.\nwi tehs/ ko manni Tehwi tsdsin-\nnufchi irr/ atpestijtchi/ ar wahr-\ndu Gosans/ un Arans/ un Re-\nzeps/ un tee Behrni Eeden/ kas\nTelaffera bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Kur irr tas Kehninsch no\nGemata? un tas Kehninsch no\nArwadas/ un tas Kehninsch no\nta Pilsfahta Sewarwaim/ Ge-\nnas un Jwas?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Kad nu Iſtijus tahs Grab-\nmatas no to Wehstnefchu Roh-\nkas dabbuja/ un tahs bij lahtijs/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Un Iſtijus peeluh\npreekſch to KUNGS/un fazzij\nKUNGS Israeta Deews /\nstarp teem Kerubim fehsch /\nween effi tas Deews wiſſu Se\nmes Walstibn/ tu effi to Deb\nfi un to Semmi darrijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Atgrees ak KUNG\nTawas Ausis/ un klausi / atw\nak KUNGS! tawas Azzis\nredsi/ un klausi Saneriba Wa\ndus/ kas Scho irr fuhtijs to d\nwu Deewu apmehdiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Pateeti ak KUNGS!\nKehnint no Affirijas irr te\nPaganns/ un winnu Sem\npohstijscht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Un irr winnu Deew\neekſch Ugguni mettufscht/ jo tee\nbija Deewi/ bet Zilweku Rol\nDarbs/ Kohks un Akmins/\npehz irr tee tohs famaitajtchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Nu tad KUNGS m\nfu Deews/ ispesti muhs jelle\nwinna Rohkas / ka twiffas W\nftibas wirs Semmes atsibst/\ntu ak KUNGS! ween par D\nwu effi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Tad fuhtijs Efaijus\nmoza Debls pee Iſtiju / un li\nfazzibt: Ta fatka tas KUD\nIsraeta Deews / par ko tu ma\npectuhdsis prett Saneribu\nKehninu no Affirijas / efmu\nklaufijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Schis irr tas Wahrt\nko tas KUNGS prett wi\nri\n"
    }
  ],
